# Environment variables for DFCL Inventory App
# Copy to .env and adjust.

# === LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ===
DATABASE_URL=file:/home/z/my-project/db/custom.db
PRISMA_DATABASE_URL=file:/home/z/my-project/db/custom.db

# === VERCEL + TURSO PRODUCTION (set on Vercel) ===
# TURSO_DATABASE_URL=libsql://your-db-handle.turso.io
# TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=eyJhbGciOi...
# (PRISMA_DATABASE_URL is auto-set by db.ts to "file:db.sqlite" when TURSO_* vars are detected)

# === CLOUDFLARE PAGES + D1 (optional) ===
# D1 binding is injected automatically.
